import React from "react";
import {Link} from "react-router-dom";
import { Container, Nav, Navbar, NavDropdown } from 'react-bootstrap';
import "./structure-styles.css"

const NavigationBar = () => (
  <Container>
    <Navbar fixed="top" bg="white" expand="lg">

      <Navbar.Toggle aria-controls="basic-navbar-nav" />
      <Navbar.Collapse id="basic-navbar-nav">
        <Nav className="headnavbar justify-content-center" style={{ flex: 1}}>
          <NavDropdown className="navbarlink" title="Aktuelles" id="basic-nav-dropdown">
            <NavDropdown.Item  href="#aktuelles">Aktuelles</NavDropdown.Item>
            <NavDropdown.Item  href="#termine">Termine</NavDropdown.Item>
            <NavDropdown.Item  href="#oeffnungszeiten">Ã–ffnungszeiten</NavDropdown.Item>
          </NavDropdown>
          {/* <Nav.Link className="navbarlink" href="/weingut">Weingut</Nav.Link> */}
          <Link to="/weingut" className="nav-link navbarlink">Weingut</Link>
          <Nav.Link className="navbarlink" href="#weine">Weine</Nav.Link>
          <Nav.Link className="navbarlink" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://loreley-kellerei.winitas-shop.de/">Shop</Nav.Link>
          <Nav.Link className="navbarlink" href="#kontakt">Kontakt</Nav.Link>
        </Nav>

        

      </Navbar.Collapse>
    </Navbar>
  </Container>


)
export default NavigationBar;
